4	External Interface Requirements

4.1	User Interface

In this section, we will describe the intermediate units that affect AR Translator Application.

4.2	Hardware Interface

System will have hardware requirements on Android and Firebase data base.

4.3	Software Interface

AR Translator project will consist of two main parts: Android studio and Firebase API. 
And some software interfaces will be added to the project.

4.4	Communication interfaces

Due to the pandemic, we only communicate online meeting or by phone.
